                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Septimio Caeser<lb break="no" n="3"/>no duplario <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XX <lb n="5"/>vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> XL <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Caesern</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Sabini<lb break="no" n="7"/>anus <expan><abbr>sig</abbr><ex>nifer</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">p(iae)? f(idelis)</supplied> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach der Auffindung im 18. Jh. in der kgl. Burg in Budapest bezeugt, wo das Monument &amp;quot;&amp;quot;beim Aufräumen des Schuttes&amp;quot;&amp;quot; (Wolfarth nach CIL III 4324) wiedergefunden wurde, vermutlich kurz nach dem Brand der Burg während der Ungarischen Revolution 1848/49. Seitdem verschollen.</p>
            </div>
